---
layout: v2/layout.njk
title: Curated Lists
permalink: "/v2/lists/"
listOrder:
  - cra-itself
  - projects
  - maintainers
  - stewards
  - manufacturers
  - standards
  - important-and-critical-products
  - attestations
  - legislation
---

<section class="section-intro">
  <p>Curated collections of FAQs organized for specific audiences and use cases. Each list contains carefully selected questions most relevant to that topic or role.</p>
</section>

<nav class="card-grid">
  {% for listId in listOrder %}
    {% for list in data.lists %}
      {% if list.id == listId %}
        <a href="/v2{{ list.permalink }}/" class="card">
          <h2>{% if list.icon %}{{ list.icon }} {% endif %}{{ list.title }}</h2>
          <p>{{ list.description }}</p>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  {% endfor %}
</nav>
